# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in your own value.
# `.env.local` is git-ignored, so your key never gets committed.
#
# Web3Forms access key for the feedback form. Get a free key at
# https://web3forms.com (it maps to the inbox you registered).
#
# NOTE: Vite inlines any VITE_* variable into the built client bundle, so this
# key is visible to anyone who inspects the deployed site. That is expected and
# safe for Web3Forms — the key can only submit to your form and never reveals
# your email address.
VITE_WEB3FORMS_KEY=
